        <num>CC 548</num>
        <heading>548.  Existence of usufructuaries</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 548.  Existence of usufructuaries.
When the usufruct is established by an act inter vivos, the usufructuary must exist or be conceived at the time of the execution of the instrument.  When the usufruct is established by an act mortis causa, the usufructuary must exist or be conceived at the time of the death of the testator.</p>
        </content>
